The evidence with the title 'Excise tax on indoor tanning services frequently asked questions ... ' says Oct 1, 2017  ... Outside of the bundled service, the operator charges $20 for each swim lesson and $15 for each tanning service, for a total regular charge of $230. The amount subject to tax for the bundled service is computed as 30/230 x 200 = $26.08. The indoor tanning tax is 10 percent of $26.08, which is $2.60. 
